title: 倔一死战插件问题
author: xiaoyumuman
txt_content:
An error occured while executing the command.Check the console
当我输入/bs join arenaid 的时候，突然显示上面的英文，我进入控制台却木有发现任何的问题。怎么解决呢？

replies.author: Jovel
replies.txt_content: 插件不允许OP获得所有权限，请根据插件教程自行修改OP获得所有权限

replies.author: xiaoyumuman
replies.txt_content:
